@{b}@{u}Foreign language support@{ub}@{uu}


   PhotoFolio supports foreign language text catalog files as introduced
with Workbench 2.1 @{b}locale.library@{ub}. If you wish to create your own
national translation table you should consult the program source code file
@{b}PhotoFolio.ct@{ub} which is a blank translation table.


   Once you have finished creating a translation table, send it to me on
disk or via eMail for everyone else to use. (If you wish!)

@EndNode

