@{b}@{u}Workbench and Shell@{ub}@{uu}


   The program can be started either from Workbench or Shell.
Kickstart 3.0 (revision 39.106 ) and Workbench 3.0 (revision 29.29)
are the minimum required to run PhotoFolio.


   The behaviour of Photofolio can be changed by adding tool type entries
to the corresponding Workbench icon or by specifying additional command
line parameters when running the program from the Shell. Supported
keywords are:


@{LINDENT 6}
	@{b}GUIGFX=(YES|NO)@{ub}

This forces Photofolio to use guigfx.library regardless of whether
CyberGraphX is installed or not.
@{PARD}


@EndNode

