This opens an ASL requester allowing you to load a previously saved
settings file.
@{PARD}


@{LINDENT 6}
	@{b}Save settings as@{ub}

This opens an ASL requester allowing you to save the current program
settings to a file.
@{PARD}


@{LINDENT 6}
	@{b}Save settings default@{ub}

This saves the current program settings in the file
PROGDIR:PhotoFolio.prefs.
@{PARD}

