Re-display the current image full size.
@{PARD}


@{LINDENT 6}
	@{b}Show half@{ub}

Re-display the current image half size.
@{PARD}


@{LINDENT 6}
	@{b}Show quarter@{ub}

Re-display the current image quarter size.
